{"tid":1999563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喜茶8間執剩2間","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T10:12:49.000Z","uid":333312,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9af9a7e29fd5ed869ca0b4e3ae46c5a5c1315c32","tid":1999563,"uid":333312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"2018年進軍香港時紅極一時的內地茶飲店「喜茶」（HEYTEA），自去年6月起爆發反修例事件，網民抵制內地品牌後，本港生意可謂一落千丈。喜茶在港有8間分店，惟近期6間分店連環停業，位於尖沙咀的3間分店更疑似全線「執笠」。本報記者今日（3日）以顧客身分致電目前正在營業、位於沙田新城市廣場的喜茶分店，職員確認喜茶目前在港仍有營運的分店只有兩間，更指其他分店「應該唔會再開」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200503&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60898762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200503%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60898762&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=19df0730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200503%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60898762&h=8b01f4b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200503&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60898762</a> <br />\n【連環停業】喜茶港8間分店只剩2間 職員：應該唔會再開"},{"pid":"0fab2b2f81d7183a1c8aa8a5c166b7852c907f55","tid":1999563,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"支那野放落肚會死嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fa7e8ad8bac9e9e6dea6de22cb38079801b1f5","tid":1999563,"uid":27047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"希望最後兩間都執埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd64b75a0df96fcafeadaf215ab561ab2fd158a","tid":1999563,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80f39bc371227e25e83547331ff11ff55a090ec7","tid":1999563,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fab2b2f81d7183a1c8aa8a5c166b7852c907f55","tid":1999563,"u